{"id": "1492396796939604039", "channel_id": "1492001442725105707", "type": 19, "author_id": "618475034465533954", "author_name": "silencio3507", "author_bot": false, "content": "There is a loud group of players who mocks anyone who wants to play on auto. I love the gameplay personally, though some of it I find tedious. My friend joined when I told her they added auto, mostly to collect characters but she has fun building them and exploring some harder content as well (train for example). This change made her not want to do bi-weeklies at all. Said it's boring for her. Meaning no upgrade materials. Meaning lack of progress. Which will probably cause her to drop the game in a few months, knowing her and she was a spender. Never heard of gacha game that introduced something for ease of the players to then remove it few patches down the line.", "timestamp": "2026-04-11T05:32:03.782000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["111974069548617728"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1492344154968031294", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1492001442725105707", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Get Auto enable for dtide", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
