{"id": "1492484255807180943", "channel_id": "1492001442725105707", "type": 0, "author_id": "239736802796109824", "author_name": "rhatsu", "author_bot": false, "content": "Removing auto was pointless, sometimes I want to tryhard and sometimes I don't have time, now I have to skip, and I lose materials because I simply don't have time, you bait new players for auto and then take it away. I haven't see any gacha that adds mechanics only to randomly remove them one day without any consultation. I don't know what you expected, that removing the auto would suddenly make people who complained start playing well? It's like suddenly removing the third wheel from a child's bike. You won't make them ride well, but they'll probably fall over and stop trying. Those who couldn't use their brains and turn off the auto in moments that were too difficult certainly won't be clearing the content now. What's more, it will probably make them stop playing, and without the resources, they'll probably abandon the game", "timestamp": "2026-04-11T11:19:35.601000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💯", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1492001442725105707", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Get Auto enable for dtide", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
