{"id": "1492544200611463189", "channel_id": "1492544200611463189", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "I want to play Liz on madness mode. I can't because the aliemus restriction is too severe. I have to use 3-4 embryos to generate enough aliemus to exalt** Liz every 3 turns. ** In medium difficulty I was exalting her every turn.\n\nThis kills this mode for me. \n\nI looked up what teams people are using - and they are card based teams. \n\nPlease remove the aliemus restrictions on madness mode. A lot of the teams I like rely on exalts and with the giant health of the bosses in madness I have to do multiple exalts because 1 isn't enough for the boss. \n\nTry a Sorel Thais team run in testing. Collect enough embyros to exalt Sorel once and see how much life you kill on a madness boss. Why did you make a mode that is all Gmurphy and Pollux?", "timestamp": "2026-04-11T15:17:47.556000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1492544200611463189", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Train mode - sucks for exalt based teams", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
